{"tid":2072512,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港國家格言","createTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T14:21:52.000Z","uid":39470,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b9ff5941e4a353f61307128c99b7ea4d0cfed3","tid":2072512,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:38.000Z","msg":"呢一刻係咪「光復香港 時代革命」？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但革命過後總要回復正常，唔好好似鄰國咁時時刻刻都係革命狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考下我地D盟友係點<br />\n<br />\n 英國：Dieu et mon droit（法語，我權天授，為王室格言）<br />\n 美國：In God We Trust（我們信仰上帝，官方格言）和E pluribus unum（拉丁語，合眾為一）（事實上）<br />\n 中華民國：無官方格言。非官方格言：三民主義。<br />\n 泰國：無，非官方格言為：ชาติ ศาสนา พระมหากษัตริย์（泰語，民族，宗教，國王）<br />\n 南韓：홍익인간（拉丁轉寫：Hongik Ingan）（韓語，弘益人間）<br />\n 越南：&ETH;ộc lập, Tự do, Hạnh ph&uacute;c（越南語，獨立，自由，幸福）<br />\n 印度：सत्यमेव जयते（拉丁轉寫：Satyameva Jayate）（梵語，唯有真理得勝）<br />\n 拉脫維亞：Tēvzemei un Brīvībai（拉脫維亞語，為了祖國與自由）<br />\n 立陶宛：Tautos jėga vienybėje（立陶宛語，民族的力量源於團結）<br />\n 愛沙尼亞：Heade &uuml;llatuste maa（愛沙尼亞語，無疑讓你驚奇無比）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%BC%E8%A8%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPducFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=d0643711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%BC%E8%A8%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a>"},{"pid":"9b961479ec42329d351725810a13003bd278f393","tid":2072512,"uid":19296,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"「願榮光歸香港」<br />\n「兄弟爬山，各有各做」"},{"pid":"f5edfc1cee970b361a292918cb2717be64fccb1f","tid":2072512,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"港人為大 香港萬歲"},{"pid":"7ede6e8f48a9d0dab44b7ff3a2964f0b5e8071f2","ti